{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #003366; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #336699; /* Lighter Blue */\n            --accent-color: #ffffff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --bg-color: #f4f7f6;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            border-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</h1>\n        <p>Fortifying Your Digital Future</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>SecureGuard is a leading cybersecurity firm dedicated to protecting businesses from the ever-evolving landscape of digital threats. We provide comprehensive, proactive, and reactive solutions tailored to your unique needs.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>\n                    <p>Identify vulnerabilities and understand your organization's risk posture.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Threat Detection & Response</h3>\n                    <p>Real-time monitoring and rapid response to contain and neutralize threats.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Penetration Testing</h3>\n                    <p>Simulate real-world attacks to uncover weaknesses before attackers do.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Security Consulting</h3>\n                    <p>Expert advice to build and maintain a robust security framework.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Employee Training</h3>\n                    <p>Educate your staff to be your first line of defense.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Incident Management</h3>\n                    <p>Swift and effective handling of security breaches to minimize impact.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to enhance your security? Contact us today for a free consultation.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@secureguard.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureGuard Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p><a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}